        <p>After installing Revenza, follow these steps to launch your first upsell offer in under 10 minutes.</p>
        <div class="steps">
          <div class="step"><div class="step-num">1</div><div class="step-body"><strong>Choose an addon</strong> — Go to Modules and enable <strong>Upsell popup</strong> or <strong>In-cart upsell</strong> to start.</div></div>
